title: Idiot Flesh (3 Albums)
description:
Experimental / Cabaret / Goth / Avant-Garde / Occult / Clown / Prog

"The group is characterized by its use of non-traditional instrumentation,
such as screwdrivers, bicycle horns, and other odd or seemingly random
objects to create their music. Their live shows featured everything from
marching band acts to puppet shows."

Some members went on the create the Sleepytime Gorilla Museum.
